Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.67,0:23:29.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撫慰兄長大人是我的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.42,0:23:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那是我的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.18,0:23:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行哦 露妮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個任務的最低條件是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.76,0:23:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最低條件是?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.43,0:23:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,D罩杯哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.06,0:23:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.52,0:23:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 我還不夠大
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.77,0:23:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油哦 露妮
